name: A trip to the bodega
description:
Owning this NFT gives you full commercial rights to the beat. You are free to use it however you please. 
Making this track made me feel like I was walking down the street to get a nice garlic-cheese manakeesh. Not a bodega specialty but it's one of the things I miss the most from Dubai.

PS: Melody is from a splice sample pack, I just made adjustments to my liking. This is an old beat that was sitting in my beats folder.
